caption: The image features a speech bubble with a motivational quote written in cursive. The quote reads, "Do things at your own pace. Life's not a race." The text is written in a light blue color, and the bubble is positioned towards the top left of the image. The background consists of a brown and orange color scheme, with a few circles scattered throughout the scene. The image is likely meant to inspire and encourage viewers to take their time and enjoy life at their own pace.
texts: "Do things at your own pace. Life's not a race."
